comments: Batum (PHI) establishes himself in Robinson's (NYK) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Robinson (NYK) cleanly deflects the ball away from Embiid (PHI) in the post.
Maxey (PHI) briefly places a hand on Anunoby's (NYK) back while the two players are airborne, but the contact does not affect his dunk at the rim.
Brunson (NYK) steps into Maxey's (PHI) path, initiating body contact that affects Maxey's SQBR during the driving shot attempt.
Maxey (PHI) commits a take foul on Anunoby (NYK). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
McBride (NYK) moves alongside Oubre Jr.'s (PHI) path and avoids making contact with him during his shot attempt.  Oubre Jr. loses his footing on his own near the basket.
Embiid (PHI) establishes himself in McBride's (NYK) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Maxey (PHI) gathers the ball on his left foot, takes two legal steps, and then moves his right foot again just before he is fouled on his shot.
Robinson (NYK) is drawn into the air by the shot fake from Maxey (PHI) and initiates illegal body contact during his jump shot attempt.
Batum (PHI) commits a take foul on Hart (NYK).
Robinson (NYK) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Maxey (PHI).
Batum (PHI) maintains a legal guarding position on Brunson's (NYK) drive and cleanly tips the ball on Brunson's shot.
After Brunson's (NYK) shot is tipped by Batum (PHI), it goes directly behind the backboard and is therefore out of bounds.
Hartenstein (NYK) establishes himself in Oubre Jr.'s (PHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Embiid (PHI) cleanly deflects the ball away from Brunson (NYK) on his drive.
Hartenstein (NYK) maintains a legal guarding position, moving along Maxey's (PHI) path during the driving shot attempt.
McBride (NYK) initiates contact to Embiid's (PHI) arm as he starts his shooting motion.
Hartenstein (NYK) establishes himself in Batum's (PHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Embiid (PHI) maintains a legal guarding position, moving along Brunson's (NYK) path before cleanly blocking the driving shot attempt.
Brunson (NYK) hooks Batum's (PHI) arm to create the illegal contact between the two players.
Embiid (PHI) makes unnecessary contact with a wind up and follow through to Brunson (NYK) on his drive to the rim.
Embiid (PHI) establishes himself in Hart's (NYK) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Hartenstein (NYK) contests Oubre Jr.'s (PHI) shot attempt near the basket and the contact to his wrist just as he releases the ball is marginal.
Oubre Jr. (PHI) moves alongside of Brunson (NYK) and marginal contact occurs with Brunson's non-shooting arm when Oubre Jr. briefly lowers his arm.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Hart (NYK) remains in bounds when he makes contact with the ball near the baseline to save it from going out of bounds.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Embiid (PHI) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Brunson (NYK) throws an errant pass out of bounds.
Brunson (NYK) commits a take foul on Harris (PHI).
Batum (PHI) moves alongside Brunson's (NYK) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Hart (PHI) commits a take foul on Maxey (PHI).
